data.description: $12,000 BUYER CLOSING COST ASSISTANCE OR RATE BUY DOWN! Welcome home to this gorgeous 2019 brick and stone home that shows like a model home, offering 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, formal dining or office & oversized game room. Open concept living area w cozy gas fireplace just in time for the Fall weather looks out over expansive backyard w privacy fence & covered patio. Enjoy your dream eat-in kitchen featuring homey touches such as window nook, walnut cabinets w glass, gas cooking, granite countertops & kitchen island. Downstairs primary suite boasts tray ceiling & natural light w primary ensuite bathroom offering soaking tub, tiled walk in shower, double vanity, separate wash room & his and hers closets. Upstairs offers oversized game room, 3 bedrooms & full bath. Conveniently located to new park with splash pad, sports fields, shopping & highly rated schools.
